# Commerce AI Tool

AI-powered product search plugin for commercetools (text, voice, image). pnpm + Turborepo monorepo.

## Packages

- `packages/core` — business logic, AI (OpenRouter/Bedrock), commercetools client
- `packages/server` — Next.js/Express handlers, ElevenLabs STT/TTS
- `packages/react` — React search widget (glass UI)
- `packages/angular` — Angular component
- `apps/demo-next` — Next.js 16 demo app

Dependencies: `server` / `react` / `angular` → `core`. API secrets stay on the server only.

## Stack

TypeScript strict, tsup, Vitest, ESLint 9, Turbo 2, pnpm 9.15.9, Node ≥ 24.

## Architecture

```
Browser → /api/commerce-ai/* (server) → core → AI + commercetools
```

Never expose API keys in client-side code.
